name: PRO Real Estate Investment Trust 8.00% convertible unsecured subordinated debentures
longDescription: PRO Real Estate Investment Trust is an open-ended real estate investment trust. The REIT's segments include three classifications of investment properties - Retail, Office, and Industrial. All of the REIT's activities are located in one geographical segment, which is Canada. Its objective is to maintain a combination of short, medium, and long-term debt maturities that are appropriate for the overall debt level of its portfolio, considering the availability of financing and market conditions, and the financial characteristics of each property. It derives key revenue from the Industrial segment.
